- , cognate_set

library(magrittr)
library(ape)

df <- read.csv("data.csv", stringsAsFactors = FALSE)

data <- df[,-c(1:3)]
row.names(data) <- paste(1:294, df$english)

data %>% 
  dist() %>% 
  hclust(method = "ward.D2") ->
  hc

plot(as.phylo(hc), 
     type = "fan",
     cex = 0.6,
     no.margin = TRUE,
     tip.color = c("red",
                   "blue",
                   "green",
                   "black",
                   "yellow",
                   "pink", 
                   "navy")[as.factor(df$cognate_set)])
